description: "Tool execution contracts — platform invocation, model resolution, tool catalog discovery, tool executor, and idempotency key resolution."
files[5]{file,type,summary}:
  ModelResolverInterface.php,interface,Resolves the target AI model configuration from message context and default settings.
  PlatformInterface.php,interface,Executes AI model invocations and returns structured provider responses.
  ToolCatalogProviderInterface.php,interface,Resolves the available tool catalog from execution context.
  ToolExecutorInterface.php,interface,Executes a tool call and returns the structured result.
  ToolIdempotencyKeyResolverInterface.php,interface,Resolves idempotency keys for tool calls to ensure consistent deduplication.